[5] China: Yunnan Province
Date: Fri 9 Apr 2021
Source: news.sina.com.cn [in Chinese, translated, edited]
https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2021-04-09/doc-ikmxzfmk5763471.shtml

Epidemic situation of the novel coronavirus pneumonia in Yunnan Province on 8 Apr 2021
As of 8 Apr 2021 24:00, the province has 87 confirmed cases (imported 3 cases, local 84 cases) and asymptomatic infection 44 cases (imported 19 cases, local 25 cases) were isolated in designated medical institutions for treatment and medical observation.

8 new confirmed cases:
Confirmed case 1: Female, 26 years old, Chinese nationality, common type
Confirmed case 2: Female, 44 years old, Chinese nationality, common type
Confirmed case 3: Female, 47 years old, Chinese nationality, common type
Confirmed case 4: Male, 34 years old, Chinese nationality, common type
Confirmed case 5: Female, 38 years old, Chinese nationality, common type
Confirmed case 6: Female, 36 years old, Thai nationality, common type
Confirmed case 7: Male, 29 years old, Chinese nationality, common type
Confirmed case 8: Female, 36 years old, Chinese nationality, mild

The above-mentioned cases were all discovered in the 2nd round of nucleic acid tests for all employees in Ruili City, which were transported to designated medical institutions by negative pressure ambulances, combined with epidemiological history, clinical manifestations and laboratory test results, and diagnosed as confirmed cases of novel coronavirus pneumonia.

[Byline: Liu Guangbo]

